traightforward pick-sense-and-place alternatives frequently fail to solve\npick-and-constrained placement problems. The proposed pipeline, however,\nachieves more than 95% success rate and faster execution times as evaluated\nover multiple physical experiments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 28 Jun 2020 04:44:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-30"}
