, so it is suggested that clinical\ntrials of masks are now carried out while continuously monitoring effects and\nside-effects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 28 Jun 2020 14:57:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-30"}
